    <section id="id45532967">
      <title>Assessment</title>
      <para id="id45532973"><emphasis effect="bold">Learning Outcome 1:</emphasis> The learner will be able to recognise, describe and represent numbers and their relationships, and to count, estimate, calculate and check with competence and confidence in solving problems.</para>
      <para id="id45532086"><emphasis effect="bold">Assessment Standard 1.10:</emphasis> We know this when the learner uses a range of techniques to perform written and mental calculations with whole numbers including:</para>
      <para id="id45533106"><emphasis effect="bold">1.10.2:</emphasis> long division.</para>
